At one time a woman whose husband was living away from home became pregnant by a lover
She said to a monk who associated with her family
Venerable please find me a method of abortion
Alright he said
and he gave her a method of abortion
The child died
The monk became anxious 
You have committed an offense entailing expulsion
At one time there was a man had two wives
one who was barren and one who was fertile
The barren one said to a monk who associated with her family
If the other wife gives birth to a son Venerable shell become the head wife
Please find a method of abortion for her
Alright he said
and he did so
The child died
but the mother did not die
The monk became anxious 
You have committed an offense entailing expulsion
