Case studies
At one time a monk had sexual intercourse with a female monkey
He became anxious thinking
The Buddha has laid down a training rule
Could it be that Ive committed an offense entailing expulsion
He told the Buddha
Youve committed an offense entailing expulsion
At one time a number of Vajjian monks from Vesālī had sexual intercourse without first renouncing the training and revealing their weakness
They became anxious thinking
The Buddha has laid down a training rule
Could it be that weve committed an offense entailing expulsion
They told the Buddha
Youve committed an offense entailing expulsion
At one time
thinking he would avoid an offense
a monk had sexual intercourse while dressed like a householder
He became anxious thinking
The Buddha has laid down a training rule
Could it be that Ive committed an offense entailing expulsion
He told the Buddha
Youve committed an offense entailing expulsion
At one time
thinking he would avoid an offense
a monk had sexual intercourse while naked
He became anxious 
Youve committed an offense entailing expulsion
At one time
thinking he would avoid an offense
a monk had sexual intercourse while dressed in a grass robe 
while dressed in a bark robe 
while dressed in a robe made of bits of wood 
while dressed in a sarong made of human hair 
while dressed in a sarong made of horsehair 
while dressed in a robe of owls wing 
while dressed in a robe of antelope hide
He became anxious 
Youve committed an offense entailing expulsion
