At one time a monk was lying down in the Jātiyā Grove at Bhaddiya having gone there for the days meditation
He had an erection because of wind
A certain woman saw him and sat down on his penis and having taken her pleasure she left
The monks seeing the moisture told the Buddha
Monks an erection occurs for five reasons
because of sensual desire because of feces because of urine because of wind because of being stung by caterpillars
Its impossible that that monk had an erection because of sensual desire
That monk is a perfected one
Theres no offense for that monk
